title: "PDF Agent: Academic PDF Question Answering System Based on Retrieval-Augmented Generation"
authors:
  - family-names: "Zeng"
    given-names: "Carter"
repository-code: "https://github.com/CarterZeng/pdf_agent"
keywords:
  - "retrieval-augmented generation"
  - "academic PDF question answering"
